(16)TH=12MHR2Ω2+12IHψ·2+12IHΩ2sin2ψ
and
(17)TPZT=12ρptpb∑a=12∑n=1Na{∑i∑j(q·iaq·ja∫PZTnaϕiaϕjadx)+ψ·∫PZTnax2dx+ψ·2∑i∑j(qiaqja∫PZTnaϕiaϕjadx)+2ψ·∑i(q·ia∫PZTnaϕiaxdx)+R2Ω2∫PZTnadx+Ω2cos2ψ∑i∑j(qiaqja∫PZTnaϕiaϕjadx)+Ω2sin2ψ∫PZTnax2dx+2RΩ2cosψ∑iqia∫PZTnaϕiadx-2RΩ2sinψ∫PZTnaxdx-2Ω2sinψcosψ∑i(qia∫PZTnaϕiaxdx)}
