The vector KH is the effects of moving spacecraft in the orbit which is defined as
(26)KH={KHψKHq}
where KHψ and KHq are obtained in Appendix A.

The vector Q is defined as
(27)Q={τ-KPeeava}
where τ is the control torque and va is the vector of actuator's voltages.

